{"type":"text","timestamp":1777038231231,"sessionID":"ses_24045021affeKAQpK4fE6xOqLW","part":{"id":"prt_dbfbb7cd2001R0Jr5DO8ZiDUWt","messageID":"msg_dbfbb7507001OaYwJKJzYiy9LP","sessionID":"ses_24045021affeKAQpK4fE6xOqLW","type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've created a fully playable Snake game in a single `index.html` file with all the features you requested:\n\n## Features Included:\n\n✅ **Arrow Key Controls** - Move the snake in all four directions\n✅ **Score Display** - Track current score, high score (saved locally), and level\n✅ **Game Over Detection** - Collision with walls and self-collision\n✅ **Restart Functionality** - Reset the game at any time\n✅ **Polished UI** - Modern gradient design with smooth animations\n\n## Game Mechanics:\n\n- **Progressive Difficulty** - Speed increases as you level up (every 50 points)\n- **Food Generation** - Food spawns randomly and never overlaps with the snake\n- **Visual Polish** - Glowing effects, gradient backgrounds, animated snake eyes that follow direction\n- **High Score Persistence** - High scores saved in browser localStorage\n- **Responsive Design** - Works on mobile and desktop\n\n## How to Play:\n\n1. Open `index.html` in your browser\n2. Click \"Start Game\"\n3. Use arrow keys to move the snake\n4. Eat the red food to grow and gain points\n5. Avoid walls and yourself\n6. Click \"Restart\" to reset without losing high score\n\nThe game is completely self-contained with all HTML, CSS, and JavaScript inline. Just open it and play!","time":{"start":1777038228690,"end":1777038231230}}}
